## REGRA 8 — COMPONENTES E TEMPLATES

**Feedback ao usuário — sempre via `ToastService`:**
```typescript
this.cpeService.rebootCpe(serial).subscribe({
  next: () => this.toastService.success('CPE reiniciada com sucesso'),
  error: () => this.toastService.error('Falha ao reiniciar CPE'),
});
```

**Loading state — usar `SkeletonComponent`:**
```html
<app-skeleton *ngIf="loading" shape="card" [count]="3" />
<div *ngIf="!loading && data">...</div>
```

**Null safety no template:**
```html
<span *ngIf="cpe?.wifi2g?.channel">{{ cpe.wifi2g.channel }}</span>
```

